===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ʧæv/}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æv|-æv]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{italbrac|British|derogatory|informal}} A working-class youth: especially as associated with aggression, poor education, and a perceived ‘common’ taste in clothing and lifestyle.
# {{italbrac|British|friendly|informal}} A label used to refer to someone who regularly dresses in casual sports clothing, has a taste for dance and pop music, and is able to talk to younger people on informal terms.

